OL,6,FChief Inspector Tom Welch said: "This
OL,7,Fis a complex police investigation, and
OL,8,Four officers are still in the very
OL,9,Fearly stages of establishing the
OL,10,Fcircumstances of this incident.J"At
OL,11,Fthis stage of our ongoing
OL,12,Finvestigation we can confirm that a
OL,13,Ffirearm was shot in the area causing a
OL,14,Fserious facial injury to a man in his
OL,15,F30s.
